Added Post-it note: "2nd Bassist???" 1. on back of photo 'Jimmy Garrett' (BN p. 198). 2. cited in JR as being 'Ray Appleton' . 3. Ashley Kahn says it's 'Lionel "Sonny" Johnson' (p. 182)". Additional added Post-it note: "Photo in JR cites 2nd bassist as "Ray Appleton"? In A. Kahn's book he's cited as "Lionel 'Sonny' Johnson". Frank Kofsky interviewed Pharoah Sanders, Rashied Ali and John Coltrane between August 16 - 19, 1966.
